<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan kal lioah lung-lawmhnak hla kha sa u si, Rau loin khuatha ah kan
 kal lai, Khua-muihnak a dih tikah ceunak a um lai, Rau loin khuatha ah
 kan kal lai.

[C1]
   A nai dengmang cang, (A nai dengmang cang) a nai dengmang cang, (a
   nai dengmang cang), Thihnak (Thihnak) tiva kan tan lai, Thlitu daih nak
   khuatha ah, kan i tong te lai, Rau loin khuatha ah kan kal lai.

[V2]
 Kal duhmi cu lamtha kha hmuhsak hna u si, Rau loin khuatha ah kan kal
 lai, Khrihfa kan unau kha dawtnak in forh u sih, Rau loin khuatha ah kan
 kal lai.

[C2]
   A nai dengmang cang, (A nai dengmang cang) a nai dengmang cang, (a
   nai dengmang cang), Thihnak (Thihnak) tiva kan tan lai, Thlitu daih nak
   khuatha ah, kan i tong te lai, Rau loin khuatha ah kan kal lai.

[V3]
 Hmailei khua ah dinhnak le hna-ngamnak a um, Rau loin khuatha ah kan
 kal lai, Khi khua chungah mitthli tlaknak zeihmanh um lo, Rau loin
 khuatha ah kan kal lai.

[C3]
   A nai dengmang cang, (A nai dengmang cang) a nai dengmang cang, (a
   nai dengmang cang), Thihnak (Thihnak) tiva kan tan lai, Thlitu daih nak
   khuatha ah, kan i tong te lai, Rau loin khuatha ah kan kal lai.

[V4]
 Hi vawleicung ah thennak kha um hmanhsehlaw, Vancung khua ah kan i
 tong than lai, Lung-lawmhnak in hla thar kha kan sa ti te lai, Zungzal
 khuatha ah khin kan um lai.

[C4]
   A nai dengmang cang, (A nai dengmang cang) a nai dengmang cang, (a
   nai dengmang cang), Thihnak (Thihnak) tiva kan tan lai, Thlitu daih nak
   khuatha ah, kan i tong te lai, Rau loin khuatha ah kan kal lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>RAU LOIN KHUA THA AH KAN KAL LAI CH446</title>
</song>